Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,DAI'S SECRET
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.46,0:01:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dragon Knight is approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.14,0:01:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He's close!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.85,0:01:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dragon Knight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Baran!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They're connected by their crests.\NHe'll reach this castle soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We must ready our defenses!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I will be the defense!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.47,0:02:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam Nabara and Meruru\Nwill stay here with Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.37,0:02:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't fight Baran and leave unscathed!\NYou'll need my healing-type spells!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not one to be\Ntalked out of your decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. Let's get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam Nabara, Meruru,\Ndon't let Dai out of his cell!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.20,0:03:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand still.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.76,0:03:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A weapon! Use it to defend yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Defend myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious? You use this to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.35,0:03:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! I can't! It's too scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it off, miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, I've told you before. You're a Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're small but brave\Nand bright and sincere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.93,0:04:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the real you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.88,0:04:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This cowardly you isn't a Hero!\NIt isn't who Dai is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.97,0:04:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true. I can't be a Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, if we wait,\Nsomeone will come to protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He instinctively senses\Nthat Baran is his father after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! He took precious\Nmemories of us from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.39,0:04:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a terrible enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be happy that he's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Leona...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight, Dai! Fight to regain what's yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.09,0:04:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Your memories and courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:04:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Courage...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, Crocodine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.91,0:05:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.95,0:05:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think... something like this....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,happened before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you aren't quite dead yet.\NBut I will not finish you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.35,0:05:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You can wallow in shame\Nand feel regret as you bleed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I must hurry and regroup\Nwith Master Baran to reclaim Master Dino.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Dino"? Does he mean Dai?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You still bother to resist?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Father or not...\NI can't let him... take Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the hope of all humans\Nliving in this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What rubbish!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.77,0:06:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The filthy humans of this world\Ndon't deserve such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.\NI shall tell you before you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason why Master Baran hates humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The only woman Master Baran ever loved,\Nin other words, Master Dino's mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,was murdered by humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The ones who killed Dai's mother\Nwere humans?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would humans...\NJust who was Dai's mother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, only one\NDragon Knight exists at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.23,0:07:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The power of a Dragon Knight\Ncan reshape the heavens and earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus only one in a generation\Ncan possess it in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.48,0:07:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When a Dragon Knight's life ends,\Nthe Holy Mother Dragon descends.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is said that she caringly cradles\Nthe battle-weary knight's body.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the Dragon Crest,\Nhaving fulfilled its duty,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is passed on to the life\Nthe Mother Dragon carries within her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A new knight now within her,\Nshe gives birth in a distant land.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The humans there worship the child\Nas a divine child and raise it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.57,0:07:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And when the knight is fully grown,\Nit awakens to its duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, no Dragon Knight ever knows\Nparent or offspring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They are destined to a life\Nof never-ending battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But something unusual happened\Nin Master Baran's generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifteen years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When Hadorra laid waste to the world,\Nthe Dragon Knight did not appear.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was a human Hero who defeated Hadorra.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.73,0:08:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Aban...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time, Master Baran\Nwas fighting a greater threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.11,0:08:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,For it is a Dragon Knight's duty to punish\Nthose who disrupt the world's balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compared to the threat of\NVeruza, King of the Abyss,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,0:08:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}who was the last intelligent Dragon\Nseeking to conquer this world,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}even Hadorra was trivial enough\Nto be ignored.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Having vanquished Veruza and his kin,\NMaster Baran was mortally wounded.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Master Baran used the last of his strength{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:09:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to reach the Fountain of Miracles\Nsaid to heal Dragon Knights.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.49,0:09:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so close...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.08,0:09:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Drink this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It is said to ease wounds and illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A human woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was Master Baran\Nand Lady Soara meeting.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Weary from battle, Master Baran\Nfound the sun in Lady Soara.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eventually, love between them blossomed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lady Soara was princess of Arukido Kingdom\Nand when Master Baran came to the palace,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the two grew even closer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:10:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But there were vassals\Nwho found this displeasing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They couldn't stand a stranger\Nwinning claim to the throne.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.13,0:10:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty, there are rumors\Nthat knight is not human.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.09,0:10:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.51,0:10:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He may be a surviving servant\Nof the Dark Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The fear of Hadorra being a recent memory,\Nthe humans banished Master Baran.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.94,0:10:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Soara...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems life with a human\Nwas never meant for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My time with you was a happy one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:11:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Don't leave us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,"Us"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.23,0:11:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Soara, are you with child?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dragon Knight...\NA bloodstained Slayer has sired a child?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that child...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It is Master Dino.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai is the child of\Na Dragon Knight and a human?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.01,0:11:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The three of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}lived quietly,\Ndeep in the forests of Teran.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Soara, what shall we name him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How about Dino? It means\N"Strong Dragon" in the Arukido language.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Dino, the Strong Dragon. A good name!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.86,0:11:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Dino!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.95,0:12:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Dino, don't worry.\NThat was scary, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the humans...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.88,0:12:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,did not let them enjoy\Ntheir days of peace for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.79,0:12:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A monster kidnapping their princess\Nwould shame their country.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Enraged, the king hunted them down\Nand surrounded them with a battalion.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,My love!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I mustn't kill any humans.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Master Baran made his decision.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, my love!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I surrender.\NBut do not harm Soara or my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. He may be a monster's spawn,\Nbut he's still my grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He cannot stay here,\Nbut I shall send him to a foreign land.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Master Baran allowed\Nthe Arukido soldiers to capture him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:13:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And Master Dino was taken from Lady Soara\Nand sent to a foreign land.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You are sentenced to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.93,0:13:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Soara... Dino... May you find happiness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Soara?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.89,0:13:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Soara!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.55,0:13:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Soara!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,M-My love...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How foolish! Why would you do this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.81,0:14:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I couldn't bear...\Nto see my father and the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,continue... such cruelty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Soara!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But... please don't hate humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all just scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough! Don't speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.71,0:14:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.51,0:14:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Find... Dino...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And live together... in peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Soara?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Soara!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.25,0:15:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That fool! To die for a monster?!\NWhat a disgrace!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A disgrace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Just who do you think you are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.31,0:15:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Begone! Begone, humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Arukido Kingdom vanished from this world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What hopelessly selfish creatures!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.65,0:15:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,To think I fought the King of the Abyss\Nto protect such swine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If I knew humans were such filth...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.24,0:15:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I never would have protected them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Baran searched the world,\Nbut he never found Master Dino.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Apparently, the ship was lost at sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It was in his deepest despair\Nthat Ban, the Dark King approached him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:16:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, "Don't you think the humans\Nshould be wiped out first?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Master Baran's sad past\Nthat he has told only me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.73,0:16:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! You still...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.53,0:16:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Larhart, you are indeed powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt I even have\Nthe strength left to stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But, after hearing that story,\NI realized I had to get back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,For Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and for Baran!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:32.55,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}BEAST KING REDEMPTION BLAST{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:37.55,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}ABAN STRASH{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,For Master Baran?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.65,0:16:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I know very well how Baran feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.78,0:16:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I, too, once lost faith\Nin the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I sold my soul to the Dark Army,\Nand sought to destroy everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.87,0:16:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But I realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:17:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No, my friends made me realize...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that there was still hope\Nfor the human world!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, I want to\Nhelp Baran realize this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.34,0:17:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I might be able to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What could you possibly know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You think Master Baran's pain\Nis something so light that you can ease?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible! I aimed for your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.49,0:17:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see through your attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.99,0:17:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I was fighting you\Nwhile saving myself to fight Baran.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.88,0:17:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I tried to keep my distance\Nwhen dodging your attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.92,0:17:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, I don't care\Nif you hit me or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:18:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what allows me\Nto barely dodge any mortal blows!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Cocky bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Where does this strength come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're faster than before!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.03,0:18:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the power a human wields\Nwhen risking his life!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't accept that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You were wise to bring the fight in close.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.51,0:19:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But once distance is gained,\Na sword cannot beat a spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.15,0:19:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt you can even move now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I could end this with a single thrust...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.32,0:19:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,but that won't satisfy my anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.23,0:19:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His Hakendisutoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.12,0:19:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel the sting of my claw once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Die a ghastly death!\NAs punishment for your nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Hakendisutoru!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:20:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got you! You fell for\Nmy final life-risking trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.47,0:20:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.59,0:20:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a good look at the shape of the Aura\Nour weapons create!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A cross?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Grand Cross!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.44,0:20:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Impossible!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was hiding a weapon\Ncharged with his Aura?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But he was completely defenseless!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.72,0:20:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Where did you hide such a weapon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This was the only weapon I had left!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That flimsy little chain?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.03,0:20:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This chain is unbreakable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.53,0:21:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a symbol of\Nthe bond of the Disciples of Avan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.33,0:21:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The bond...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Using Grand Cross\Nleaves me weak for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.\NThis time I'll pierce your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.73,0:21:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Drop your weapon!\NOtherwise, I crush the boy's skull!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.92,0:21:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You dirty...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.87,0:22:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.30,0:22:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you face the devil\NWith logic on your side{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:07.38,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatoe akuma ni seiron kazashite\Nmukatte mitemo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.43,0:22:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It may just be a rationalization{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:11.35,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sore wa akumade seitouka\Nsashite chigai wa naikamo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.39,0:22:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even now, even now I waver{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:15.43,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima mo ima mo yureteiru kedo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.48,0:22:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far will we go?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.60,0:22:19.48,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wa dokomade yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.53,0:22:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I heard a voice like an angel's whisper{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.65,0:22:22.78,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tenshi no sasayaki nimo nita\Nkoe ga kikoeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.82,0:22:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe it was an imposter's illusion\NIt still rang in my ears{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.94,0:22:26.70,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hatamata petenshi no mayakashi\Nhitokiwa mimi ni hibiiteita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.74,0:22:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Exposed to love and sorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:30.41,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni hiai ni sarasare nagara{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.45,0:22:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the path strewn with pride{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.57,0:22:34.70,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hokori mamire michi no tochu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.41,0:22:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fleeting moments of cowardice{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.41,0:22:38.75,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kiete wa ukabu touhikou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The SOS I held back{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:42.54,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nomikonda SOS{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.13,0:22:48.13,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}furueru te wo nigirishimeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.13,0:22:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I clenched my trembling fist{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:53.72,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatta hitotsu no chiisana yakusoku ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That single little promise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.77,0:22:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those trivial little memories{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.89,0:22:57.52,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}honno sasaina omoidetachi ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.57,0:22:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're still in my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.69,0:22:59.81,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}itsumade tattemo kono mune wo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.86,0:23:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As embers that keep me burning{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:03.98,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kogashi tsuzukeru tomoshibi ni naru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.03,0:23:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A single transparent beam of light{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.15,0:23:08.49,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitosuji no toumei na hikari ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.53,0:23:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lights the way before me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.65,0:23:11.66,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}me no mae wo terashite yuku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.70,0:23:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is little that I can do{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.82,0:23:16.33,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku ni dekiru koto wa ikutsu mo naisa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.38,0:23:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just keep on to the future\NI managed to grasp through my faith{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.50,0:23:22.54,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shinjinuita saki ni te ni shita mirai wo\Nsusunde yuke{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.85,0:23:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After a fierce battle, Larhart entrusts\NHyunckel and Popp with his last wish.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.18,0:23:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meanwhile, Dragon Master General Baran\Nfinally arrives at Teran Castle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.69,0:23:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crocodine risks his life to face Baran,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.66,0:23:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but Baran eventually reveals\Nhis true power full of grief and rage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.16,0:23:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.46,0:23:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Baran's Rage"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.21,0:23:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
